CSS3 
----
Cascading Style Sheet
    - CSS1 : 1996 
            Netscape vs IE (Internet Explorer)

    - CSS2 : 1998
        penyesuaian di tampilan printer
    
    - CSS3 : Animasi 3D, media

# Fitur CSS3
-------------
- REM Value 
    satuan 1 rem = 16px

    contoh p { font-size: 0.75rem }

- Background-size : menentukan ukuran gambar Background
    contoh 

        background-size: auto (gambar ditampilkan sesuai ukuran asli)
        background-size: cover (gambar akan menutupi seluruh container)
        background-size: contain (gambar ukuran sesuai ratio dan gambar terlihat)
                container -> 8:9 (180px 90px)
                gbr bg    -> 15:9 (150px 90px)
                gbr background tampil seluruhnya. menyisakan ruang kosong 30px

        background-size: {lebar} {tinggi}
        background-size: 75px 75px;
        background-size: 75% 75%;

- CSS Animation
    minimal versi browser yg mendukung:
        chrome >= 43
        ie >= 10
        firefox >= 16
        safari >= 9
        opera >= 30

        contoh : 
            div {
                animation-iteration-count: 2;
            }
        animation-name
        animation-duration
        animation-timing-function: linear | ease | ease-in | ease-out
                                    ease-in-out | initial | inherit
        animation-delay
        animation-iteration-count
        animation-direction: normal | reverse | alternate | alternate-reverse |
                            initial | inherit

        animation-fill-mode
        animation-play-state

    - Pseudoclass
        :first-child  -> menentukan style khusus untuk elemen pertama (<li>)
        :last-child -> menentukan style khusus untuk elemen terakhir (<li>)
        :nth-child(x) -> menentukan style khusus untuk elemen ke-x (<li>)
        :nth-child(odd) -> menentukan style khusus untuk elemen genap (<li>)
        :nth-child(even) -> menentukan style khusus untuk elemen ganjil (<li>)
        
        :first-letter -> menerapkan style pada karakter pertama

    Box-Shadow -> Efek Shadow/Bayangan pada Box
    Text-Shadow -> Efek Shadow/Bayangan pada Text

    Border-radius -> membentuk sudut element
    Gradient-Background -> linear 
                            radial

    3D-Transform
        rotateX()
        rotateY()
        rotateZ()

HTML5 
------
- Doctype ditulis sebelum tag <html>
HTML5:
<!DOCTYPE html>

HTML:
<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.01//EN" "http://www/w3/org/TR/html4/strict.dtd">

- Tag figure dan figcaption
- Type Link & JS
    HTML: 
        <script src="path/script.js" type="text/javascript"></script>

    HTML5: 
        <script src="path/script.js"></script>
- ID & Class
    HTML: 
        <p class="myClass" id="myID" >
    
    HTML5: 
        <p class=myClass id=myID >

        <p class="myClass1 myClass2" id=myID >

- UL Editable
- Placeholders -> tipe input : text, search, url, tel, email, password
- Required, Readonly, Autofocus

- Audio: mp3, ogg, wav
- Video: mp4, ogg, WebM

- Atribut Data -> menyimpan kustomisasi data 
    <element data-*="value">
- Tag Semantic:
    <aside>
    <article>
    <details>
    <figure>
    <figcaption>
    <footer>
    dll




Explore: https://www.w3schools.com/
        









